for gnuplot to work

(1) Install Xming. 
(2) execute export DISPLAY=:0 nameOfProgram (for example export DISPLAY=:0 gnuplot)


-------------------------
python3 -m venv ~/venv
source ~/venv/bin/activate
pip install numpy

# to exit
deactivate


in bashrc, add this line: source ~/venv/bin/activate  


for python3 to work 

(1) After installing Xming. Set it up
(2) In ~/.bashrc, export DISPLAY=:0
(3) source ~/.bashrc



